<activity xml:id="act-calabazasGigantes" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>A and F D and G E and B H and J I and C</p>
<p>Sample response: A and F match because both show a total of 84 with 12 in each group (or for each seedling). We don’t know how many groups (or seedlings) there are.</p>
  </solution>


